reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 12, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great little iron.
reviews.reviewText: Compact, easy to use, effective. This is everything I hoped and dreamed for lol. It's super small but works kinda better than my big free standing steamer. It heats up fast and steams really well. It doesn't spit which is nice.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 18, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars I love this travel steamer iron!!!!
reviews.reviewText: I purchased a mini travel steamer iron to keep my clothes neat while on the go. Firstly, its compact design is very convenient for portability, easily fitting into the suitcase without taking up much space. The heating speed is also fast, allowing me to start using it within a few minutes.This iron is straightforward to operate—just add water and turn on the switch. The steaming effect is satisfactory, effectively removing wrinkles from clothes, making them look refreshed. It is especially suitable for handling compact clothing during travels.Despite its small size, the water tank capacity is sufficient for the needs of short-term travel. However, if frequent use or handling more clothes is required, it is advisable to use it moderately due to the limited water tank capacity.Overall, this Travel Steamer Iron for Clothes Mini is a practical travel companion, making it a good choice for travelers who need to keep their clothing tidy on the go.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 6, 2024
reviews.reviewText: In terms of convenience, this small iron ticks all the boxes. It heats up incredibly fast, allowing me to start ironing within seconds. reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 29, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars YOU NEED THIS STEAMER IRON! It’s Worth it!
reviews.reviewText: The media could not be loaded. Needed to travel 5 hours to deliver a dress for a Quinceanera, and this iron/steamer 100% added to my professionalism and peace of mind! Not just to steam the dress before putting it on but also creating neat and flat pleats for the corseted top. If you are a designer, stylist, sewist of any sort YOU NEED THIS IRON! And if you aren't you still need this! Its nice and sleek, heats up quickly (im talking less than 20 seconds or quicker), the plate it sits on is perfect, its easy to store, clean and travel with. The handle turns to the side..I am obsessed and have so many people asking me about it. Very affordable and 10/10 will continue to recommend this for anyone.
